title: BBC Sportscene - SPFL 720p 50fps 11.03.2018
description:
Introduced by Jonathan Sutherland.  
 
Highlights from the weekend's Scottish Premiership. It's a weekend of big derby matches with the latest installment of the Old Firm between Celtic and Rangers, while in the capital emotions run high as Hibernian host Hearts. Elsewhere, there is a Tayside derby as Dundee entertain St Johnstone, and a battle between Lanarkshire rivals Hamilton and Motherwell. Meanwhile, Aberdeen travel to Glasgow to take on Partick Thistle and Kilmarnock host Ross County.
